description is not present for all the api's in this lib file.. please add it.

Instead of saying dot can we say decimal format?

Reading value is in decimal format.
e.g: 10.34

Value before dot is considered as an integer reading value and after dot is considered as fractional reading value.

is of size

change 16bytes to 16 bytes.. where ever applicable
If sensor name is more than 16 bytes then truncate sensor name to 16 bytes  and return decoded sensor name else return the decoded sensor name as it is.
